## Testing with Time

```ruby
test "article is published at scheduled time" do
  future_time = 1.day.from_now
  article = Article.create(
    title: "Scheduled",
    body: "Body",
    published_at: future_time
  )
  
  travel_to future_time do
    assert article.published?
  end
end

test "article expires after 30 days" do
  article = articles(:old)
  
  travel 31.days do
    assert article.expired?
  end
end
```

